address in the DNS answers:</p><code>[{"name": "answers.ip", "value":
"92.24.47.250", "type": "location", "data": {"city": "Socotra", "continent":
"Asia", "coordinates": [-25.4153, 17.0743], "country": "YE", "desc":
"Yemen"}}]</code>""" ;
            sh:nodeKind sh:BlankNodeOrIRI ;
            sh:order 22 ;
            sh:path ocsf:enrichments ],
        [ sh:class ocsf:HttpResponse ;
            sh:description "Details about the HTTP response, if available." ;
            sh:maxCount 1 ;
            sh:nodeKind sh:BlankNodeOrIRI ;
            sh:order 3 ;
            sh:path ocsf:http_response ],
        [ sh:datatype xsd:string ;
            sh:description """The confidence, normalized to the caption of the confidence_id value. In the
case of 'Other', it is defined by the event source.""" ;
            sh:maxCount 1 ;
            sh:nodeKind sh:Literal ;
            sh:order 50 ;
            sh:path ocsf:confidence ],
        [ sh:class ocsf:Malware ;
            sh:description "A list of Malware objects, describing details about the identified malware." ;
            sh:nodeKind sh:BlankNodeOrIRI ;
            sh:order 57 ;
            sh:path ocsf:malware ],
        [ sh:class ocsf:HttpRequest ;
            sh:description "The HTTP Request from the proxy server to the remote server." ;
            sh:maxCount 1 ;
            sh:nodeKind sh:BlankNodeOrIRI ;
            sh:order 10 ;
            sh:path ocsf:proxy_http_request ],
        [ sh:datatype xsd:long ;
            sh:description """The end time of a time period, or the time of the most recent event included in
